metadata.name: Kibbutz DAO
metadata.description:
4,500 portrait photos of Kibbutz Kfar Haruv's members were collected from the community's archive and up-to-date photos. The data was inserted into an artificial intelligence software (GAN); the output - 25,000 new Kibbutz members.

MP4 - 256 x 256 px - 13:54 mins

This NFT is connected to a physical object (framed lenticular print) and will be shipped to the winning bidder.
